==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pilot flag
<hw>Pilot flag</hw>. <def>The flag hoisted at the fore by a vessel
desiring a pilot, in the United States the union jack, in Great Britain
the British union jack with a white border.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

